   <topic>API_GETMACHINENAME Function</topic>
   <syntax>Name_String as C = API_GetMachineName()</syntax>
   <description>Returns the name of the current computer.</description>
   <discussion>
API_GETMACHINENAME() returns the name of the host computer.
Limitations: Desktop applications only.
   </discussion>
   
   <example>
   <![CDATA[API_GETMACHINENAME() -> "Server01"]]>
   </example>
   
